B

BeanUtils - Class in org.atgel.util
Can be used to safely get properties from a bean, map, repositoryItem Example: String merchantName = (String)BeanUtils.getNestedProperty(commerceItem,"auxiliaryData.catalogRef.merchant.merchantName"); String shippingMethod =(String)BeanUtils.getNestedProperty(merchantGroup, "commerceItems[0].shippingGroupRelationships[0].shippingGroup.shippingMethod"); this will not throw a NullPointerException in any of the elements in the graph even if they are null.
